{"title":"NewStarCTF2023Misc week1","uid":"278eb56d6b73097353a4349ddc3a6411","slug":"NewStarCTF2023 MiscWEEK1","date":"2023-11-23T04:24:14.996Z","updated":"2023-11-23T04:24:15.001Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/NewStarCTF2023 MiscWEEK1.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"WEEK1\"><a href=\"#WEEK1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"WEEK1\"></a>WEEK1</h1><h2 id=\"CyberChef-s-Secret\"><a href=\"#CyberChef-s-Secret\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CyberChef&#39;s Secret\"></a>CyberChef&#39;s Secret</h2><p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/SlADFSEVyAAjmd1A.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>cyberchef一把梭得到flag</p>\n<p><strong>flag{Base_15_S0_Easy<em>^</em>^}</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"机密图片\"><a href=\"#机密图片\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"机密图片\"></a>机密图片</h2><p>得到一张二维码</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/5E0ukxYfJrjxhyQ3.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>扫描了一下没东西，发现是lsb隐写，zsteg一把梭</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/MSCVb1maxJpMciYX.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p><strong>flag{W3lc0m3_t0_N3wSt4RCTF_2023_7cda3ece}</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"流量！鲨鱼！\"><a href=\"#流量！鲨鱼！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"流量！鲨鱼！\"></a>流量！鲨鱼！</h2><p>分析流量包，导出http对象中发现了可疑文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/fm8MJgsyGuRqYssW.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>保存下来得到一串base64编码，解码得到flag</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/aMfWX3QeG9Y8ksle.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p><strong>flag{Wri35h4rk_1s_u53ful_b72a609537e6}</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"压缩包们\"><a href=\"#压缩包们\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"压缩包们\"></a>压缩包们</h2><p>得到一个无后缀文件，拖入winhex查看</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/7eopXjr01zh0fhFd.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>发现是一个缺失头的压缩包，手动修复</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/ooZnTdBacElb4Uiw.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>保存后解压下一个flag.zip，解码注释可以知道压缩包密码是6位数，但是这里显示压缩包损坏（并且显示未加密），证明没有修复完全，对照着加密正确的加密压缩包进行修补</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/zSIKOKXfdXFVbVSG.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>得到修复好的压缩包</p>\n<p>使用ARCHPR进行爆破得到密码</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/9QudM0ynKfBMOXsZ.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>解压得到flag</p>\n<p><strong>flag{y0u_ar3_the_m4ter_of_z1111ppp_606a4adc}</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"空白格\"><a href=\"#空白格\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"空白格\"></a>空白格</h2><p>点开附件发现是空白的，用sublime打开</p>\n<p>选中之后发现有东西</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/0vrGzyTSd4q4pXXg.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>whitespace加密</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://vii5ard.github.io/whitespace/\">https://vii5ard.github.io/whitespace/</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/u69KZXXiR3uNmvd3.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>得到flag</p>\n<p><strong>flag{w3_h4v3_to0_m4ny_wh1t3_sp4ce_2a5b4e04}</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"隐秘的眼睛\"><a href=\"#隐秘的眼睛\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"隐秘的眼睛\"></a>隐秘的眼睛</h2><p>看题目就知道是考silenteye了，直接使用默认密码</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/b9F1RVI5uAVxKGLI.png!thumbnail\"></p>\n<p>得到flag</p>\n<p><strong>flag{R0ck1ng_y0u_63b0dc13a591}</strong></p>\n","text":"WEEK1CyberChef&#39;s Secret cyberchef一把梭得到flag flag{Base_15_S0_Easy^^} 机密图片得到一张二...","permalink":"/post/NewStarCTF2023 MiscWEEK1","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":672,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"MISC","slug":"MISC","count":10,"path":"api/categories/MISC.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"MISC","slug":"MISC","count":10,"path":"api/tags/MISC.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#WEEK1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">WEEK1</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#CyberChef-s-Secret\"><span class=\"toc-text\">CyberChef&#39;s Secret</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%BA%E5%AF%86%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\"